        <br />✔️ Refreshing beverages and mocktails to complement your meals
    </p>
    <hr />
    <h2>🏆 Why Choose Taste Hub?</h2>
    <p>
        <ul class="ul1">
            <li> Experience since 2015 – nearly a decade of trusted service</li>
            <li>Handpicked ingredients to ensure freshness and quality</li>
            <li>Skilled chefs with a passion for perfection</li>
            <li>Friendly ambiance that makes you feel at home</li>
